<html lang="en">
  <%-include('./modules/head')%>
  <body>
    <%-include('./modules/nav')%>
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Integration Guide for Cryptic Payment System</h1>
      <p>This guide will help you integrate the Cryptic payment system into your website.</p>
  
      <h2>Step 1: Add the Stylesheet</h2>
      <p>Add the following line into the `<head>` of your HTML page:</p>
      <pre><code>&lt;link rel="stylesheet" href="http://localhost:3000/stylesheets/widget.css" /&gt;</code></pre>
  
      <h2>Step 2: Add the Payment Button</h2>
      <p>Add the following line where you want the payment button to appear:</p>
      <pre><code>&lt;button id="payWithCrypticBtn" class="btn btn-primary"&gt;Pay with Cryptic&lt;/button&gt;</code></pre>
  
      <h2>Step 3: Add the Payment Processing Script</h2>
      <p>Add the following script to your page. This script will process the payment when the button is clicked:</p>
      <pre><code>
  &lt;script&gt;
    document
      .getElementById("payWithCrypticBtn")
      .addEventListener("click", function () {
        // Get destination and amount from the vendor's website
        var destination = "<%=user.sub%>"; // Replace with actual destination
        var amount = 0.0001; // Replace with actual amount
  
        // Redirect user to Cryptic website with confirmation data
        window.location.href =
          "http://localhost:3000/confirm-payment?destination=" +
          encodeURIComponent(destination) +
          "&amount=" +
          encodeURIComponent(amount);
      });
  &lt;/script&gt;
      </code></pre>
      <p>Remember to replace the `amount` variable with your own value.</p>
    </div>
    <!-- Optional JavaScript -->
    <!-- jQuery first, then Popper.js, then Bootstrap JS -->
    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.3.1.slim.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/popper.js/1.14.7/umd/popper.min.js"></script>
    
    <script
  src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"
  integrity="sha384-YvpcrYf0tY3lHB60NNkmXc5s9fDVZLESaAA55NDzOxhy9GkcIdslK1eN7N6jIeHz"
  crossorigin="anonymous"
></script>
  </body>
</html>
